sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI Pipeline
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as kserve-webhook-server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as kserve-controller-manager
    participant KnativeAPI as Knative Serving API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Storage as S3/GCS/Azure<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant StorageInit as storage-initializer<br/>Init Container
    participant LocalVolume as /mnt/models<br/>Filesystem
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>8012/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Agent as kserve-agent<br/>Sidecar
    participant Runtime as Serving Runtime<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Client as External Client

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,LocalVolume: Flow 1: Model Deployment via InferenceService
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply -f inferenceservice.yaml<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+ K8s token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+ API Server cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated InferenceService
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+ API Server cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation OK
        K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created

        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService CRs<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+ SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService event
        Controller->>KnativeAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+ SA token
        KnativeAPI-->>Controller: Service created

        Note over StorageInit,LocalVolume: Pod initialization phase
        StorageInit->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+ AWS SigV4/GCP SA
        Storage-->>StorageInit: Model files
        StorageInit->>LocalVolume: Write model files<br/>Filesystem
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: Inference Request (Serverless Mode)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+ OAuth2 token (optional)
        Gateway->>Activator: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8012 mTLS Service mesh
        Activator->>Agent: Inference request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
        Agent->>Runtime: Forward to runtime<br/>HTTP/8080 localhost
        Runtime->>LocalVolume: Read model files<br/>Filesystem
        LocalVolume-->>Runtime: Model data
        Runtime->>Runtime: Execute inference
        Runtime-->>Agent: Prediction result<br/>HTTP/8080 localhost
        Agent-->>Activator: Response<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
        Activator-->>Gateway: Response<br/>HTTP/8012 mTLS
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 3: Multi-Model InferenceGraph Request
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/graph:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+ OAuth2 token (optional)
        Gateway->>Router: Route to InferenceGraph<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
        Router->>InferenceServiceA: Call Model A<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS
        InferenceServiceA-->>Router: Model A result
        Router->>InferenceServiceB: Call Model B with A's output<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS
        InferenceServiceB-->>Router: Model B result
        Router-->>Gateway: Final result<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 240)
        Note over Agent,Controller: Flow 4: Logging and Monitoring
        Agent->>KnativeEventing: Send CloudEvents<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS
        Runtime->>Prometheus: Expose metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS /metrics
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create events<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+ SA token
    end
